Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.81,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慫是罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:24.52,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}腦力激盪滴滴答答 選一種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:26.98,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雲隙中一陣細雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:30.03,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不亞至高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:33.57,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女心它陰晴不定 可愛且無敵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:36.12,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像雜亂無章的鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:43.37,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜歡才算是戀愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:47.09,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱著我直到我想睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.63,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像是科幻片般的白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:55.68,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親吻我 打破劇中沉默吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.10,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優柔寡斷也好 抱緊我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:00.77,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胸口悶得難受好難受好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:05.60,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心動無法預測
Comment: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:09.07,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.36,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起勇氣來呀 My darling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:15.99,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止於歡樂和欣喜 都取決於我們自己
Comment: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.28,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:21.54,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}轉過來看著我吧 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:30.92,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意到我純粹的愛呀
